Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:30.47,DarkMHS_JP,,0,0,0,,時はまだあちこちにあるワン
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:36.78,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,おっ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.17,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,みらい リコ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.22,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,はーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:55.08,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,オレ...サッカーが
